import Item from './item' import React from 'react' import AnimationForFilter from '../utils/animation-for-filter' import ReactDOM from 'react-dom' import { items, setItems, prodcutAmount } from '../utils/product-items' import { getDataByFilter2 } from '../firebase/connect' import { filterKeyword } from '../utils/filter-keyword' import { numbers, setNumbers } from '../utils/pagination' export default function Products() { function handdleClick(value) { getDataByFilter2(filterKeyword[0], filterKeyword[1], 'products', 'products', value) } function amountOfPagination() { for (var i = 1; i <= Math.ceil(prodcutAmount / 4); i++) { numbers.push( handdleClick(i)}>{i}) } setNumbers(numbers.map((v, i) => { return handdleClick(i+1)}>{i+1} })) return numbers } amountOfPagination() return (

SHOP ALL

FILTER BY

{numbers}
 ) }
